@startuml
title Communication Diagram: Reset Password

skinparam shadowing false
allow_mixing
skinparam linestyle default
skinparam nodesep 100
skinparam ranksep 100

' --- 1. Participants ---
actor "User / Admin" as User
object "RequestResetView" as ReqView
object "SetNewPasswordView" as SetView
object "AuthController" as Controller
object "AuthService" as Service
object "MailService" as Mail
object "UserDataWrapper" as UserDB

' --- 2. Layout Skeleton ---
' User ở trên cùng, Controller ở giữa, 2 View 2 bên
ReqView -[hidden]right- User
User -[hidden]right- SetView

ReqView -[hidden]down- Controller
SetView -[hidden]down- Controller

Controller -[hidden]down- Service
Service -[hidden]left- Mail
Service -[hidden]right- UserDB

' --- 3. Messages ---

' == Flow 1: Request Token ==
User ..> ReqView : enter email
ReqView ----> Controller : 1: forgotPassword(email)
Controller ----> Service : 1.1: createResetToken(email)
Service .left.> Mail : 1.1.1: sendResetLink(token, email)
Service .up.> Controller : 1.2: request ok
Controller .up.> ReqView : 1.3: notify email sent

' == Flow 2: Set New Password ==
User ..> SetView : open link\nenter newPass
SetView ----> Controller : 2: resetPassword(token, newPass)
Controller ----> Service : 2.1: validate token +\nupdatePassword(newPass)
Service .right.> UserDB : 2.1.1: updatePasswordInDB()
UserDB .left.> Service : 2.1.2: ok
Service .up.> Controller : 2.2: success
Controller .up.> SetView : 2.3: notify success

@enduml